############ Pycharm Short -cuts ############

ctrl + option + o for organize imports
shift + command + f -> search files / texts in the whole project
shift + command + o -> open class / file etc
shift + command + u -> toggle string case
shift + command + up/down arrow -> move lines(codes) up/down

option + command + fwd/back arrow -> go back and forward between files

ctrl + r -> find and replace in the file
Fn + command + F12 -> see all the functions names in the file/class


## Virtual env in Python based application:-

python3 -m venv /path/to/new/virtual/environment
source /path/to/new/virtual/environment/bin/activate
pip3 freeze > requirements.txt ( check pipreqs )
deactivate

pip3 install -r requirements.txt  # Pip install to requirements.txt

